21 (2) ONE REPRESENTATIVE OF THE COMMISSION ON
22 ENVIRONMENTAL JUSTICE AND SUSTAINABLE COMMUNITIES;
23 (3) ONE REPRESENTATIVE OF THE POWER PLANT RESEARCH
24 PROGRAM IN THE DEPARTMENT OF NATURAL RESOURCES;
